<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>비밀번호 확인</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dongle&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Dongle', sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      background-image: url('https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/cmseu8/btq6Z9KJYXo/aDlzENDratLaBwK2MYrPF1/img.jpg');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      background-attachment: fixed;
      color: antiquewhite;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header {
      padding: 50px 0 20px;
      font-size: xx-large;
    }
    form {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    input {
      font-family: Dongle;
      font-size: xx-large;
      width: 60%;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: none;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    button {
      font-family: Dongle;
      font-size: xx-large;
      padding: 10px 40px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: none;
      background-color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>🔐 글 삭제를 위해 비밀번호를 입력하세요</h1>
  </header>

  <form action="/board/<%= id %>/delete/check" method="POST">
    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호 입력" required><br>
    <button type="submit">확인</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>
